= Access Control - Extension Proposal =

(Based on existing functionality detailed at AccessControl)

== New Requirements ==

 * Assigning rights by user groups (not just by user).
 * Lock down of the an 'extra' field, so that only authorized users can make it a particular value. 
 e.g. Only 'FCO editors' and 'admins' can set the 'department' field to the value 'Foreign and Commenwealth Office'.
